@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lddkqu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(v1)
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.abs(v1 + 0.52) + (v2 + 0.39 / tmp + 0.05)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.88)))
    v0 = v2
    v2 = 0.65
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.24) * (v2 + 0.83))
    tmp = 0.95
    data[tid] = v0
